_sText:
<center>
![](http://imageshack.us/m/839/7058/aimsealevel.png "aim_sealevel")
----------------------------------------------------

Here's my map aim_sealevel. The map takes place in the middle of the Pacific Ocean in a medium sized arena.
Each player gets a Scout at the start of the round and has the opportunity to get one of four AWP on each sides and three HE grenades which are laying right in the center of the map.
The map plays like most aim_ maps and there are enough wooden boxes to take cover at. 

- 32 Players (16CT/16T)
- HDR Ready
- Cubemaps are build
- Bot nav file is included

How to install:

Copy both the .bsp and the .nav into:

"Steam\SteamApps\Username\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps"

I hope you have fun with my map and please leave feedback so I can improve my skills.
</center>
